overview: loonsh.com is emerging Indian e-commerce company which offers guaranteed low prices and huge discount on vast product range loonsh.com is an Indian e-commerce company, an online auction and shopping website in which people and businesses buy and sell a broad variety of goods and services. Founded in Pune, India to bridge the gap between online and offline world, loonsh.com offers diversified, product range such as Books, Mobile Phone, DVDs, CDs, computer software, video games, electronics, apparel, furniture, food, toys and much more. It also provides free shipping to its Pune customers on all its products.
